--[[
    Soundscape Catalog (lib/soundscape_catalog.ttslua)

    Static definitions for layered, non-positional audio. Runtime control lives in
    core/soundscape.ttslua; future weather/site/calendar systems should express
    intent through that module instead of playing AssetBundle effects directly.

    Effect names are the external contract with the Unity AssetBundle and must
    match `.dev/Soundscape & Audio/Audio Tracks.md` exactly, including casing.
]]

